by my positive choices.

13:33.980 --> 13:36.981
♪ 'Cause I'm the best baby
that they never gotta keep ♪

13:36.983 --> 13:40.118
♪ One, two, three,
they gonna run back to me ♪

13:40.120 --> 13:41.119
